'''Yâ-sû Kâ-thìn''' he [[Ngi-sṳ̍p sṳ-ki]] song-pan ya̍p tshai [[Chûng-koet]] tshut-hien ke yit-kiên tshung-yeu ke [[Kî-tuk-kau]] [[Lìn-ên-phai]] [[Chûng-kau]] thòn-thí, thi̍t-phe̍t tshái-tshí Kî-tuk-kau [[Khiung-sán tsú-ngi]] ke Vû-thok-pâng thòn-thí sên-fa̍t mù-yong. Yâ-sû Kâ-thìn he Chûng-koet li̍t-sṳ song vì-thu̍k ke yit-tshṳ Kî-tuk-kau [[Vû-thok-pâng yun-thung]]. Tshiùng [[1921-ngièn]] tshai [[Sân-tûng-sén]] [[Thai-ôn]] tshóng-phan, to-liáu [[1952-ngièn]] pûn Chûng-koet tsṳn-fú kié-san ，tshièn-heu khiung-yû tshṳ̀-siu̍k sâm-sṳ̍p ngièn sṳ̀-kiên, fûn-phu thi-khî tha̍t-tó kiú-ke sén-fun.

